@startuml
!pragma teoz true
!pragma sequenceMessageSpan true
participant A
participant B
participant C
autonumber 1.02:003 2
A -[#DodgerBlue;line.dotted;line.thickness=4]>> B : %autonumber% long label with enough words to exercise message span wrapping deterministically
& B -[#orange;line.dashed]->o C : parallel circle
autonumber inc A
C x-[#red;line.thickness=5]-> A : increment-first
|||80|||
ref over A, C
  multiline reference body
  stays inside participant span
end ref
A -\\ B : lower half head
B -/ C : upper half head
@enduml
